sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Avis Budget Group Inc (Symbol: CAR), where a total of 29,897 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 3.0 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 45.3% of CAR's average daily trading volume over the past month of 6.6 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $8 strike put option expiring August 21, 2020, with 11,107 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 1.1 million underlying shares of CAR.
